[{"id":"VR111268","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VR111264.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div>\n\n<div>The purpose of the note is to tell Xiao Mei how to</div>\n","rubricRef":"VR111268_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\">\n<p class=\"introduction passage-intro\"><em><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Please note, on the exam administered each May, the Listening multiple-choice questions appear first and the Reading multiple-choice questions appear second.</span></span></em></p>\n\n<p class=\"introduction passage-intro\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"introduction passage-intro\">Read this note.</p>\n\n<div class=\"passage\" xml:lang=\"zh\">\n<div class=\"letter letter_type:note style:1\">\n<p class=\"letter_salutation\">小妹：</p>\n\n<div class=\"letter_body\">\n<p class=\"passage_para\">我不在的這幾天，家裏就交給你了。順便說一下，扔垃圾的時候，玻璃瓶、塑料盒、罐子和紙製品之類的垃圾要扔到綠色的可回收垃圾桶裏。還有，扔玻璃瓶和塑料盒以前，要洗乾淨然後再扔。其他的垃圾都可以扔到藍色的垃圾桶裏。有什麼事給我打電話，我過幾天就回來！多謝！</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"letter_signature\">\n<p class=\"signature_line\">大姐</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"letter letter_type:note style:1\">\n<p class=\"letter_salutation\">小妹：</p>\n\n<div class=\"letter_body\">\n<p class=\"passage_para\">我不在的这几天，家里就交给你了。顺便说一下，扔垃圾的时候，玻璃瓶、塑料盒、罐子和纸制品之类的垃圾要扔到绿色的可回收垃圾桶里。还有，扔玻璃瓶和塑料盒以前，要洗干净然后再扔。其他的垃圾都可以扔到蓝色的垃圾桶里。有什么事给我打电话，我过几天就回来！多谢！</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"letter_signature\">\n<p class=\"signature_line\">大姐</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">prepare food</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">wash the dishes</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">sort household waste</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">clean the house</p>"],"answer":2}]